REFERENCE VARIABLES
Efficiency (E)
Home Position (HP)
Opponent Position (OP)

STATIC VARIABLES
Base (B) = 100
Position Coeficient (p) = 10

DERIVED VARIABLES
Position Offset(PO) = (HB-OP)

-----------------------------------
SINGLE ATTACK EFFICIENCY FORMULA
-----------------------------------
E = B+(PO*p)+[(N+(PO*s)]*p